    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just... it makes me wonder if that's the best way for them to go out. if they just sat there and let the darkness take them, would that be better than trying to fix a broken world that's already gone? like, is there any reason to keep trying to hold on if the end is just going to be more peaceful than the struggle?",
